解：注意到 \((3x^2-2x+7)' = 6x-2 = 2(3x-1)\)，凑微分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int(3 x-1) \sqrt{3 x^{2}-2 x+7} dx &= \frac{1}{2} \int \sqrt{3 x^{2}-2 x+7} d\left(3 x^{2}-2 x+7\right) \\
&= \frac{1}{3}\left(3 x^{2}-2 x+7\right)^{3 / 2}+C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(\frac{1}{3}\left(3 x^{2}-2 x+7\right)^{3 / 2}+C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：将被积函数变形拆分，再分别积分：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int x(1-x)^{n} dx &= \int [1-(1-x)](1-x)^n dx \\
&= \int(1-x)^{n} d x - \int(1-x)^{n+1} d x \\
&= \frac{-(1-x)^{n+1}}{n+1}+\frac{(1-x)^{n+2}}{n+2}+C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(\frac{-(1-x)^{n+1}}{n+1}+\frac{(1-x)^{n+2}}{n+2}+C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：令 \(t=sin^2 x\)，则 \(dt = 2\sin x \cos x dx = \sin2x dx\)，代入积分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int \frac{sin 2 x}{1+e^{sin ^{2} x}} dx &= \int \frac{d sin^2 x}{1+e^{sin^2 x}} = \int \frac{dt}{1+e^t} \\
&= \int \frac{e^{-t} dt}{e^{-t}+1} = -\int \frac{d e^{-t}}{e^{-t}+1} \\
&= -\ln \left(1+e^{-t}\right)+C = -\ln \left(1+e^{-sin^2 x}\right)+C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(-\ln \left(1+e^{-sin^2 x}\right)+C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：令 \(t=\sqrt[4]{\tan x}\)，则 \(\tan x = t^4\)，\(x=\arctan t^4\)，\(dx=\frac{4t^3}{1+t^8}dt\)，且 \(\sin^2 x = \frac{\tan^2 x}{1+\tan^2 x} = \frac{t^8}{1+t^8}\)，代入积分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int \frac{\sqrt[4]{tan x} d x}{sin ^{2} x} &= \int \frac{t \cdot \frac{4t^3}{1+t^8} dt}{\frac{t^8}{1+t^8}} = 4 \int \frac{t^4}{t^8} dt = 4 \int t^{-4} dt \\
&= 4 \cdot \frac{t^{-3}}{-3} + C = -\frac{4}{3} (\tan x)^{-3/4} + C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(-\frac{4}{3} (\tan x)^{-3/4} + C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：令 \(t=\sqrt{x+1}\)，则 \(x=t^2-1\)，\(dx=2t dt\)，\(x^2-1=t^2(t^2-2)\)，代入积分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int \frac{ln \left(x^{2}-1\right)}{\sqrt{x+1}} d x &= 2 \int \ln\left(t^2(t^2-2)\right) dt \\
&= 4 \int \ln t dt + 2 \int \ln(t-\sqrt{2}) dt + 2 \int \ln(t+\sqrt{2}) dt
\end{aligned}
\]

利用分部积分公式 \(\int \ln u du = u(\ln u -1) + C\)，逐项积分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int \frac{ln \left(x^{2}-1\right)}{\sqrt{x+1}} d x &= 4t(\ln t -1) + 2(t-\sqrt{2})[\ln(t-\sqrt{2})-1] + 2(t+\sqrt{2})[\ln(t+\sqrt{2})-1] + C \\
&= -8 \sqrt{x+1} + 2 \sqrt{x+1} \ln(x^2-1) + 2 \sqrt{2} \ln \frac{\sqrt{x+1}+\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{x+1}-\sqrt{2}} + C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(-8 \sqrt{x+1} + 2 \sqrt{x+1} \ln(x^2-1) + 2 \sqrt{2} \ln \frac{\sqrt{x+1}+\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{x+1}-\sqrt{2}} + C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：先对分母因式分解，\(x^4+x = x(x^3+1) = x(x+1)(x^2-x+1)\)，拆分部分分式：
\[
\frac{1}{x^4+x} = \frac{1}{x} - \frac{1}{3(x+1)} - \frac{2x-1}{3(x^2-x+1)}
\]
逐项积分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int \frac{1}{x^{4}+x} d x &= \int \frac{1}{x} dx - \frac{1}{3}\int \frac{1}{x+1} dx - \frac{1}{3}\int \frac{2x-1}{x^2-x+1} dx \\
&= \ln|x| - \frac{1}{3}\ln|x+1| - \frac{1}{3}\ln|x^2-x+1| + C \\
&= \frac{1}{3} ln \left|\frac{x^{3}}{x^{3}+1}\right| + C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(\frac{1}{3} ln \left|\frac{x^{3}}{x^{3}+1}\right| + C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：先化简被积函数：
\[
\frac{1+\tan x}{\sin2x} = \frac{1+\frac{\sin x}{\cos x}}{2\sin x \cos x} = \frac{\cos x + \sin x}{2\sin x \cos^2 x} = \frac{1}{2\sin x \cos x} + \frac{1}{2\cos^2 x}
\]
拆分积分得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int \frac{1+tan x}{sin 2 x} d x &= \frac{1}{2}\int \frac{1}{\sin x \cos x} dx + \frac{1}{2}\int \sec^2 x dx \\
&= \frac{1}{2}\int \frac{1}{\tan x} d\tan x + \frac{1}{2}\tan x + C \\
&= \frac{1}{2} ln |tan x| + \frac{1}{2} tan x + C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(\frac{1}{2} ln |tan x| + \frac{1}{2} tan x + C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)

解：先分部积分，令 \(u=\ln\frac{1+x}{1-x}\)，\(dv=x dx\)，则 \(du=\left( \frac{1}{1+x} + \frac{1}{1-x} \right)dx = \frac{2}{1-x^2}dx\)，\(v=\frac{1}{2}x^2\)，得：
\[
\begin{aligned}
\int x \ln \frac{1+x}{1-x} d x &= \frac{1}{2}x^2 \ln\frac{1+x}{1-x} - \int \frac{x^2}{1-x^2} dx \\
&= \frac{1}{2}x^2 \ln\frac{1+x}{1-x} + \int \left(1 - \frac{1}{1-x^2}\right) dx \\
&= \frac{1}{2}x^2 \ln\frac{1+x}{1-x} + x - \frac{1}{2}\ln\left|\frac{1+x}{1-x}\right| + C \\
&= \frac{1}{2}(x^2-1)\ln\frac{1+x}{1-x} + x + C, C \in \mathbb{R}
\end{aligned}
\]

最终答案：\(\frac{1}{2}(x^2-1)\ln\frac{1+x}{1-x} + x + C\)，\(C \in \mathbb{R}\)
